<!--pages/More/About/about.wxml-->
<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="black-cover"></view>
    <image class="logo" src="/images/more/logo.png"></image>
    <image class="title" src="/images/more/title.png"></image>
  </view>
  <view class="content">
    <view class="version">
      <view class="version-title">
        <text class="title-name">掌上交理</text>
        <text class="version-text">{{version}}</text>
        <text class="version-text">模型协会招新</text>
      </view>
      <view bindtap="toggleLog">
        <text class="version-log-link update-log" wx:if="{{!showLog}}">更新日志</text>
        <text class="version-log-link" wx:else>简介</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="describe" wx:if="{{!showLog}}">
      <text class="desc-title">简介</text>
      <view class="desc-list">
        <text class="desc-list-item">模型协会qq群：607124905</text>
        <text class="desc-list-item">学校官网：http://www.ecjtuit.com.cn/</text>
      </view>
      <text class="desc-content">掌上交理是一款微信小程序，由学校社团《模型协会》开发，有别于公众号的一种全新的连接用户与服务的方式，无需下载与安装即可在微信内被便捷地获取和传播，同时具有出色的使用体验。</text>
    </view>

    <view class="log-list" wx:else>
      <view class="describe">
        <view class="desc-title">
          <text class="desc-v">v0.0.7 先行版</text>
          <text class="desc-time">2017.9.19</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">修复BUG</text>
        <view class="desc-list">
          <text class="desc-list-item">修复ios课表显示界面bug</text>
          <text class="desc-list-item">修复ios表单提交界面bug</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="describe">
        <view class="desc-title">
          <text class="desc-v">v0.0.6 先行版</text>
          <text class="desc-time">2017.9.18</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">修复BUG</text>
        <view class="desc-list">
          <text class="desc-list-item">修复聊聊功能头像不存在等bug</text> 修复ios课表显示界面bug
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="describe">
        <view class="desc-title">
          <text class="desc-v">v0.0.5 先行版</text>
          <text class="desc-time">2017.9.15</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">优化完善</text>
        <view class="desc-list">
          <text class="desc-list-item">将资讯界面改成实验室界面</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="describe">
        <view class="desc-title">
          <text class="desc-v">v0.0.4 先行版</text>
          <text class="desc-time">2017.9.13</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">修复BUG</text>
        <view class="desc-list">
          <text class="desc-list-item">修改首页课表鬼畜抽动问题</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">优化完善</text>
        <view class="desc-list">
          <text class="desc-list-item">增加考试、补考安排缓存</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="describe">
        <view class="desc-title">
          <text class="desc-v">v0.0.3 先行版</text>
          <text class="desc-time">2017.9.12</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">修复BUG</text>
        <view class="desc-list">
          <text class="desc-list-item">修复ios系统显示时间周数问题</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="describe">
        <view class="desc-title">
          <text class="desc-v">v0.0.2 迎新版</text>
          <text class="desc-time">2017.9.5</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">个人暂时不能发布学校新闻资讯,暂时取消该页面功能</text>
      </view>
      <view class="describe">
        <view class="desc-title">
          <text class="desc-v">v0.0.1 迎新版</text>
          <text class="desc-time">2017.9.1</text>
        </view>
        <text class="desc-content">模型协会招新</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="footer">
    <view class="footer-lanshan">
      <image src="../../images/core/xiehui_logo.png"></image>
      <text>模型协会 · JM工作室</text>
    </view>
    <text>Copyright @ {{year}} All Rights Reserved</text>
  </view>
</view>